short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Go from light mode to dark mode on Testudo!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This chrome extension allows you to go from light mode to a dark mode theme on Testudo the University Of Maryland's class site! All you have to do is click on the extension in the toolbar and click the button on the popup window!
